<threat_model>
## Trust Boundaries

| Boundary | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| init_extension at LOAD ↔ all subsequent callbacks | After Plan 06, init_extension owns NO duckdb_connection — every callback derives its own per-call from `*context.db` |
| Structural guard test ↔ future commits | The Rust unit test runs on every cargo build/test cycle; CI enforces the invariant |

