| Threat ID | Category | Component | Disposition | Mitigation Plan |
|-----------|----------|-----------|-------------|-----------------|
| T-65-06-01 | Tampering | Future commit reintroduces a long-lived duckdb_connect into init_extension | mitigate | `init_extension_has_no_duckdb_connect` Rust unit test (Task 1) fails CI immediately. |
| T-65-06-02 | Tampering | Future commit caches a `duckdb_database` in a module-level OnceLock or thread_local | mitigate | `no_module_level_oncelock_or_thread_local` test (Task 1) fails CI. |
